<br>
I look back over the names posting here and I have memories of late nights with my guildies helping some of you get your epics completed.  I see names of people for whom I have answered dozens of questions and have retrieved corpses.  And I also see several I have never spoken to who have no idea who I am or what I am about.  Regardless of this, I learn one thing, all of that help, answers, and aid I have offered means nothing to some of you.  As well, I learn that even if someone knows nothing at all of me, they are comfortable speaking to me in this manner.  But then, this is how we learn, right?  <br>
<br>
Just a single favor I have to ask of a few of you:  Please stop sending me tells apologizing for the obnoxious things you have posted here.  Please stop asking me not to take it personally, that it is &quot;just your guild, not you&quot;.  You see, it does not work that way for me.  I raid with these people because I respect them.  If you show them this sort of disrespect, you are showing it to me as well.  That being the case, I do take it quite personally.   <p>Phal Phototrophic <BR>
Lvl 60 Thief of the Family Jewels <BR>
Dark Horizon</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm11.showMessage?topicID=234.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm11.showMessage?topicID=245.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm11.emailToFriend?topicID=248.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm11.threadControl?topicID=248.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=248.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm11.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=248.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub41.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thecrossroadstavern8833frm31">ANNOUNCEMENTS<option value="thecrossroadstavern8833frm8">The Tavern<option value="thecrossroadstavern8833frm4">Raid Planning and Discussion<option value="thecrossroadstavern8833frm11">Flame Forum<option value="thecrossroadstavern8833frm32">Thanks and Praise<option value="thecrossroadstavern8833frm34">Bottom Feeders<option value="thecrossroadstavern8833frm6">Non-EQ Discussions<option val